article.headline: Cal St.-Fullerton 106, UC Davis 95
article.story: DAVIS, Calif. -- Guard Josh Akognon scored 29 points including seven 3-pointers to lead Cal State Fullerton over UC Davis, 106-95, on Saturday. Aaron Thompson added 19 points and Gerard Anderson scored 18 for the Cal State Fullerton Titans (13-12, 7-6 Big West). UC Davis guard Vince Oliver led the Aggies (11-14, 6-6 Big West) in scoring with 32 points. Forward Joe Harden added 15, and guard Mark Payne 14 points for the Aggies. The Titans' Anderson also pitched in with nine rebounds, and center Ray Miller had nine points and seven boards.
